        </mj-text>

        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-color="lightgrey" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section mj-class="body-section">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="10px">Dear {{first_name}},</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px"
          >Yes! Thank you for opting into our official Beta Tester program. Your
