          latest product â€” Busha Commerce â€” while we (well, 2-3 people on the
          Busha Research team) will observe your interaction to take feedback.
          Easy peasy.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px"
          >This entire exercise should take about 30 minutes (or less). Because
          this will be done virtually, there are three (3) things for you to
          note:</mj-text
        >

        <mj-list padding-left="8px" padding-bottom="10px">
          <mj-li>
            <div style="padding-bottom: 10px">
              <span style="font-weight: 600"
                >You will need to have your video camera and mic turned on</span
