            </div></mj-li
          >
          <mj-li>
            <div style="padding-bottom: 10px">
              <span style="font-weight: 600"
                >You will need to turn on screen sharing</span
              >
              so we can observe as you interact with the product.
            </div>
          </mj-li>
          <mj-li>
            <div style="padding-bottom: 10px">
              <span style="font-weight: 600"
                >You will need to complete a pre-determined list of tasks</span
              >
              that will be provided e.g, Create A Checkout Link.
            </div></mj-li
          >
        </mj-list>

        <mj-text>
          Also, you will be asked a few questions about how your experience went
          afterwards. Further instructions will be provided on the day.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section mj-class="body-section">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px" font-weight="700"
          >What are your next steps?</mj-text
        >

        <mj-text padding-bottom="10px" padding-left="10px"
          >1. Ensure youâ€™ve read through the
          <a
