          >2. Choose your preferred date and time for the usability testing. You
          can
          <a
            href="https://calendly.com/d/2pd-fnq-39k/busha-commerce-usability-research"
            style="color: #12a633"
            target="_blank"
            >use this link</a
          >.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="10px"
          >3. Get your laptop charged and your camera screen cleaned
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text padding-bottom="0px"
          >Please note that you can choose to opt-out at any time, no pressure.
          But to receive the reward, you will need to have contributed at least
          80% of the required time into the session.</mj-text
        >
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section mj-class="body-section">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button
          align="left"
