    <mj-section mj-class="body-section">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding-bottom="20px">
          Thank you for your continued support of Busha.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>#LiveMoreWithCrypto </mj-text>
        <mj-text> Busha Research ðŸ’š. </mj-text>

        <mj-divider
